# 📊 Detailed Insights

## 1. Revenue Trends
Sales increased over time with noticeable seasonal peaks, especially toward the end of the year.

## 2. Product Performance
High-value technology products contributed the most to overall revenue.

## 3. Regional Analysis
The West region outperformed all others in profitability, while some regions lagged behind.

## 4. Category Performance
- Technology: High profit
- Office Supplies: Stable
- Furniture: Low margins

## 5. Key Issues
- Over-discounting reduced profitability
- Some high-sales products had low profit margins

## 6. Recommendations
- Optimize pricing strategy
- Focus on high-performing regions
- Improve low-margin product categories
